# Third-Party Dependencies

This folder contains external utilities from official repositories.

## Contents

### qwen/
Utilities from the official Qwen model repositories:
- `qwen_omni_utils.py`: Utilities for Qwen Omni models (from Qwen2.5-Omni repo)

## Setup

To install the third-party package in your environment:

```bash
cd /home/miao/spatial-reasoning
pip install -e third-party
```

## Sources

- **qwen_omni_utils.py**: https://github.com/QwenLM/Qwen2.5-Omni
